==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Incognita
<hw>In*cog"ni*ta</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Incognito</er>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>A woman who is unknown or in disguise.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The state of being in disguise; -- said of a
woman.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Incognitant</ent>⟦br⟧
